               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930410-12-cd66" type="crimeDate">15th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-12-off65 t17930410-12-cd66"></join>, four linen aprons, value 6 s. three linen<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179304100015"></xptr>diaper table cloths, value 6 s. a linen napkin, value 1 s. a linen wrapper, value 10 d. a vicker basket, value 3 d. the goods of 
                     
